<i>noun</i>: 중상모략 [중상모략], 음해 [음해] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>중상모략 [중상모략]</dt><br>
<dd>slandering; false accusation</dd><br>
<dd>남을 해치려고 근거 없는 말로 욕하고 속임수를 써서 일을 꾸미는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of plotting to harm someone by making groundless accusations against him/her and using tricks.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>음해 [음해]</dt><br>
<dd>slandering</dd><br>
<dd>몸을 드러내지 않고 남에게 해를 가함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of doing harm to someone without appearing in person.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>